治目的支殖民....特別關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解支共毫無底線攻擊香港人<br />\n唔怕你二三十年後都長期報復?<br />\n正係因為佢預左殖民換血<br />\n所有支殖民完全係支共爪牙, 沒有一個是磨菇<br />\n雙非由2000年江澤民時代就舖路<br />\n漏口佳十年前就爆左句臨界點<br />\n反送中只係民怨之一<br />\n抗爭者唔承認呢點反而玩死自己<br />\n關心支殖民<br />\n支殖民自己都唔敢再殖入香港<br />\n人口唔被換血, 你先可以長期對港共篤眼篤鼻<br />\n就算改變唔到支共消滅香港既意志<br />\n起碼可以係被消滅之前完成最大報復"},{"pid":"d973c808581e3c26387c6dbb7e9acb2fb0305513","tid":2350347,"uid":313334,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5dfafd478888c309f037756608d9876c556beb74","tid":2350347,"uid":263183,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ff28e59627367fd61fa396217bbbe47d2c0dc5e6","tid":2350347,"uid":216907,"like":10,"dislike":19,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"242be9dc8b01c7d3d8dcddcf18a5f232667087ab","tid":2350347,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"係咪針對攬鈔巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"辛苦巴打星期六係連登打國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"打？一樣野都爭取唔到<br />\n打你老母？"},{"pid":"bb4c5213aa8e9104a2ec471be016d3e06e350e91","tid":2350347,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔：我地移民係打國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班留港撚繼續交稅俾港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad67a5f81c156f1b1770e1fad38927af788ed885","tid":2350347,"uid":44285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d973c808581e3c26387c6dbb7e9acb2fb0305513","tid":2350347,"uid":313334,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid"